####Number of people with diabetes reaches 4.7 million
One in ten over 40s now has Type 2 diabetes, and the number of people living
with diabetes in all its forms in the UK has reached 4.7 million. The number
of people affected by diabetes is expected to reach 5.5 million by 2030.
